Description: Recently my family has been subjected to numerous medical bills. Although we are not desperate I am selling certain instruments to ease the burden. The following Made In Japan 2016 Ibanez is one. Recently PRS introduced The John Mayer Silver Sky (STRAT) however the Ibanez Talman Prestige as shown with Seymour Duncan pickups with the Classic-Plus Maple neck is every bit as effective as any custom quality STRAT or STRAT like instrument available at a much more reasonable price. This instrument is in excellent condition with no issues onthe body or neck and only some very modest swirls on the pickguard. Thetranslucent finish as opposed to the opaque finish shows the beautiful grain of the wood. And naturally the guitarplays like a dream. Ships with original case. Specific details are as follows: Neck type : Talman Classic-Plus Maple neck Body: Alder body Fretboard: Rosewood fretboard w/White dot inlay Fret: Medium frets Bridge: IFX-PRO bridge Neck pickup: Seymour Duncan® Alnico II Pro™ (S) neck pickup (Passive/Alnico) Bridge pickup: Seymour Duncan® Alnico II Pro™ (S) bridge pickup (Passive/Alnico) Factory tuning: 1E, 2B, 3G, 4D, 5A, 6E Finishes: Vintage White String gauge: .010/.013/.017/.026/.036/.046 Nut: Bone nut Hardware color: Chrome Case/bag: Hardshell case included NECK DIMENSIONS Scale : 648mm/25.5" a : Width-41mm at NUT b : Width-57mm at 21F c : Thickness-21mm at 1F d : Thickness-22mm at 12F Radius : 305mmR Manufacturer's Description Classic Tone meets Ibanez Performance - Ibanez has reached back in time to resurrect one of its most requested models of the past two decades. True to the original of the early 90's, today's Talman brings with it a familiar yet fresh sound that places it squarely at the crossroads of modern Ibanez innovation and cherished traditional tone.
Title: Ibanez Talman Prestige TM1730M Solid Electric Guitar w/ Case - Vintage White
